description: Rarely available corner penthouse at Dahlgren Hall, offers an opportunity to live in the heart of South Boston w/all the modern amenities you could desire.  Built in 2015, this home features soaring ceilings and generous windows throughout, allowing for sensational natural light and city views. Sleek chef's kitchen with waterfall island offers seating for 3, stainless steel appliances and opens to living and dining areas with gas fireplace. The primary suite is a private retreat, complete with a balcony, seating area, custom walk-in closet, and spa like primary bath w/rain head shower. A spacious second bedroom offers views of the city, and easy access to a second full bath with tub & shower. Unit highlights include central A/C, in-unit laundry, ample storage space, and a bonus storage room. The penthouse comes with two garage parking spaces. Residents enjoy the large common roof deck, elevator and common lounge with full kitchen, making Dalghren Hall exceptional place to live.
